I haven't worked out how to have comments in the included style file mymacros.sty
So the version with commentary is here:

% This is used for pdf compilation from qmd.
% This file should be updated in parallel with mymacros.sty which is used for html compilation.
% This is how the two files are included in the _quarto.yaml header of the qmd file
%format:
